    "description": "The Media OS for Claude Code. One plugin, 106 production-grade skills spanning FFmpeg, companion CLI tools, OBS Studio, GStreamer/MediaMTX, broadcast IP (NDI/OTIO/HDR dynamic/DeckLink/gphoto2), control protocols (MIDI/OSC/DMX/PTZ), system audio routing (PipeWire/JACK/CoreAudio/WASAPI), VFX (USD/EXR/OIIO), CV (OpenCV/MediaPipe), WebRTC (W3C + Pion/mediasoup/LiveKit), and 2026 open-source AI (upscale/interpolate/matte/depth/TTS/image-gen/video-gen/music-gen/lipsync/OCR/denoise/tagging). Strict OSI-open + commercial-safe license filter on every AI model; NC / research-only models explicitly documented-and-dropped.",
